{
    "_type": "export",
    "__export_format": 4,
    "__export_source": "opencode",
    "__export_date": "2026-07-15",
    "__export_size": 1,
    "resources": [
        {
            "_type": "workspace",
            "_id": "__WORKSPACE__",
            "name": "TechStore Explorer API",
            "description": "# TechStore Explorer API\n\n## Como obtener el token\n\nEjecuta en la terminal del proyecto:\n\n```bash\nphp artisan tinker\n```\n\nDentro de tinker:\n\n```php\n$user = \\App\\Models\\User::first();\n$user->createToken('insomnia')->plainTextToken;\n```\n\nCopia el token y pegalo en el env `token`."
        },
        {
            "_type": "environment",
            "_id": "__ENV__",
            "name": "Base",
            "data": {
                "base_url": "http://localhost:8000",
                "token": ""
            },
            "color": "#0077C0"
        },
        {
            "_type": "request_group",
            "_id": "__GRP_FAVORITES__",
            "name": "Favoritos",
            "description": "Endpoints para gestionar productos favoritos",
            "environment": {}
        },
        {
            "_type": "request",
            "_id": "__REQ_USER__",
            "name": "Obtener usuario autenticado",
            "parentId": "__WORKSPACE__",
            "method": "GET",
            "url": "{{base_url}}/api/user",
            "headers": [
                {
                    "name": "Accept",
                    "value": "application/json"
                }
            ],
            "authentication": {
                "type": "bearer",
                "token": "{{token}}"
            },
            "description": "Devuelve los datos del usuario autenticado con el token de Sanctum."
        },
        {
            "_type": "request",
            "_id": "__REQ_LIST__",
            "name": "Listar favoritos",
            "parentId": "__GRP_FAVORITES__",
            "method": "GET",
            "url": "{{base_url}}/api/favorites",
            "headers": [
                {
                    "name": "Accept",
                    "value": "application/json"
                }
            ],
            "authentication": {
                "type": "bearer",
                "token": "{{token}}"
            },
            "description": "Devuelve la lista de productos favoritos del usuario autenticado."
        },
        {
            "_type": "request",
            "_id": "__REQ_ADD__",
            "name": "Agregar favorito",
            "parentId": "__GRP_FAVORITES__",
            "method": "POST",
            "url": "{{base_url}}/api/favorites",
            "headers": [
                {
                    "name": "Accept",
                    "value": "application/json"
                },
                {
                    "name": "Content-Type",
                    "value": "application/json"
                }
            ],
            "authentication": {
                "type": "bearer",
                "token": "{{token}}"
            },
            "body": {
                "mimeType": "application/json",
                "text": "{\n    \"product_id\": 5,\n    \"product_data\": {\n        \"title\": \"Producto Ejemplo\",\n        \"price\": 100,\n        \"image\": \"https://via.placeholder.com/300\",\n        \"category\": \"Electronics\"\n    }\n}"
            },
            "description": "Agrega un producto a favoritos. `product_data` es opcional."
        },
        {
            "_type": "request",
            "_id": "__REQ_DELETE__",
            "name": "Eliminar favorito",
            "parentId": "__GRP_FAVORITES__",
            "method": "DELETE",
            "url": "{{base_url}}/api/favorites/{{id}}",
            "headers": [
                {
                    "name": "Accept",
                    "value": "application/json"
                }
            ],
            "authentication": {
                "type": "bearer",
                "token": "{{token}}"
            },
            "description": "Elimina un favorito por su `product_id`. Reemplaza `{{id}}` con el product_id.",
            "parameters": [
                {
                    "name": "id",
                    "value": "5",
                    "description": "ID del producto (product_id)"
                }
            ]
        }
    ]
}
